Download TIGER shapes for Polygon Edges

Source: R/polygon_edges.R
tt_polygon_edges.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Polygon Edges

Usage

tt_polygon_edges(state, county, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPs, postal codes, or full name of states.

county

FIPs codes or full name of counties. Optional.

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_polygon_edges('DE', county = '001')
